        <br />
        For the first time, <strong>UBC CS</strong>,
        <strong>IEEE</strong>, and <strong>Engineering
        Physics</strong> are teaming up to offer companies access
        to a greater portion of the student body than ever before.
        Our combined career fair means a better opportunity for 
	Tech companies to meet with as many as 2000 Computer Science 
	and Engineering students attending our career fair!

        <br />
        <br />
